Detailed Description

Reads and generates the indexing structures used to read the Shapefile. This is an Abstract class and is not directly instantiated, it is inherited by the Shapefile class.

Constructor & Destructor Documentation

ShapeDotNet.GIS.ShapefileReader.ShapeIndex.ShapeIndex (  string  filename,
MapMetrics  metrics
) 
 

Constructor of the ShapIndex class. It reads the .shp & .shx files and sets up the feature data structures. It parses the header of the .shx file, reads the entire .shx file and then reads the .shp file.

Parameters:
filename The filename the shapefile we want to load.
metrics The MapMetrics object for this Map.
